  interactLabel: F - Under Bed
  dialogues:
  - "Hmm... It looks like I saw something sparkling under the bed\u2026 Oh yeah!
    Now thinking about it, I haven't check what's under the bed yet."
  - Oh?!.... It looks like there's something down here
  - Okay!! Here it goes!!!!.... Hmmm?! A Teddy Bear?!.... This isn't what I expected!!
  - "Hmmm?!.... Is that the bears' eyes?!.... Well\u2026. They are barely hanging
    on after all\u2026. "
  - "Now you look at it, other than the missing eyes, the bear looks\u2026. Limp\u2026.
    Scarred\u2026. Worn & beat-down\u2026. It\u2026. Its broken"
  - "Seeing this teddy bear in this state\u2026. I really can't help but feel bad\u2026.
    I\u2026. I feel I have to do something about it"
